<br>
I have tried this and nulify magic and pumice do not work that way. They remove buffs but not the top two.  It appears they remove the weakest buffs fist. On the casters realm sight the cancel magic series are described as removing buff counters. The higher level spells remove more counters.  This seem to be the way it works from my experience.<br>
<br>
Are there some pre nerf pumice or wands in the game that remove the top two buffs period?  If so seem way unbalancing to me.  <br>
